ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Assetbundle
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
function onLoad()
  HaroScripts = [[
  -- nothing
  -- nothing
  ]]
  WebRequest.get("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ScornMandark/gundam-tts-assets/main/HaroCreator.ttslua",

          function(request)
      if request.is_error then
        log(request.error)
      else
         HaroScripts = request.text
      end
    end)
            local function ResetHaro()

              self.setName('Haro')
              self.setLuaScript(HaroScripts)
              self.reload()
              self.locked = true
              self.interactable = true

            end
            Wait.frames(ResetHaro, 60)
          end
